name: Keiba Saisho no Housoku '96 Vol. 2: GI-Road
overview: Keiba Saisho no Housoku '96 vol.2 - GI Road is the third game in the Keiba Saisho series for the Playstation console. In the game the player can only go through different stats of horses, places & jockeys. the game is heavy on japanese text, so only people that can fully understand japanese will like this game. The game features the updated stats of the end of the year season.
